{"tid":2416711,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"遭擊斃緬甸男孩傳為義務急救員 仰光護衛員遭轟頭死亡","createTime":"2021-02-21T09:23:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T15:15:14.000Z","uid":48083,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"69a3a10f55387a360e0311f7617070d629a4ffed","tid":2416711,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T09:23:38.000Z","msg":"緬甸第二大城市曼德勒周六（20 日）的反軍事政變示威，有警員向示威者開槍，導致至少兩人死亡，共中一名 16 歲男孩，頭部中槍死亡，網上盛傳他是一名義務急救員。另外，自由亞洲電台報道，昨晚再有一名護衛員遭警察行刑式擊斃。<br />\n<br />\n曼德勒血腥鎮壓事件在網上引發很大迴響，雖然緬甸軍方仍然實施網禁，除所有社交媒體被禁外，昨日傳出以任何語文登入維基網站均被禁止，惟網上仍廣泛流傳有關 16 歲男孩遭警察射爆頭骨的相片，網民紛紛致意悼念。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳男孩名為 Wai Yan Tun，16 歲，在反政變示威中自願當義務急救員，拯救傷者，但卻被軍警槍殺，頭骨爆裂，據網民引述有份為他進行急救的人表示，男孩在死前自稱「son」，是當地後輩對長輩用字，以示尊敬，並說了最後一句話：「我覺得自己不行了（I don't think I can make it）。」<br />\n<br />\n....路透又引述自由亞洲電台報道，周六晚仰光一名晚間護衛員不知何故被警察射殺。報道指事件引發社區恐慌，紛紛加派護衛員。<br />\n<br />\ntw // blood,violence,death.Happening now in shwepyithar,yangon ,Myanmar!The military shot an innocent civilian who&rsquo;s guarding his neighborhood with real bullets to the head. Who do we call for help when the police themselves are murdering us ? #Feb20Coup #WhatsHappeningInMyanmar <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/NhLVX1t42q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FNhLVX1t42q&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=91040bd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/NhLVX1t42q</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash; Honey Nway Oo (@HNwayoo) February 20, 2021<br />\n緬甸名模 Paing Takhon 在社交媒體強烈譴責軍方行為，他指軍警是蓄意向和平示威者、義務救助者開槍，指軍警已經成為恐怖分子，不單在爆發示威的地方使用暴力，亦在民居動武，甚至向救護車開槍。他呼籲各國政府保護緬甸人民，又指「這不是內戰，這是持械軍警殘害手無寸鐵的人民。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E9%81%AD%E6%93%8A%E6%96%83%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%A9%E5%82%B3%E7%82%BA%E7%BE%A9%E5%8B%99%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91%E5%93%A1-%E4%BB%B0%E5%85%89%E8%AD%B7%E8%A1%9B%E5%93%A1%E9%81%AD%E8%BD%9F%E9%A0%AD%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%2596%2583%25E7%25B7%25AC%25E7%2594%25B8%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%25A9%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%258B%2599%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%2595%2591%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E4%25BB%25B0%25E5%2585%2589%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E8%25A1%259B%25E5%2593%25A1%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25BD%259F%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%2F&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=7a86d91f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%2596%2583%25E7%25B7%25AC%25E7%2594%25B8%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%25A9%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%258B%2599%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%2595%2591%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E4%25BB%25B0%25E5%2585%2589%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E8%25A1%259B%25E5%2593%25A1%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25BD%259F%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%2F&h=f5091257\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E9%81%AD%E6%93%8A%E6%96%83%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%A9%E5%82%B3%E7%82%BA%E7%BE%A9%E5%8B%99%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91%E5%93%A1-%E4%BB%B0%E5%85%89%E8%AD%B7%E8%A1%9B%E5%93%A1%E9%81%AD%E8%BD%9F%E9%A0%AD%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1/</a>"},{"pid":"5364a42c6bcfad603ac22d1e64698660d7951c42","tid":2416711,"uid":165749,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T09:26:17.000Z","msg":"人類係高智慧生物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e184b58dc11a487168e0fa3f0a1dfefd651b09c7","tid":2416711,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T09:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />rip"},{"pid":"d9678deead18915107b51272839d4869ebd2867c","tid":2416711,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202